//
// 1. PWS_BIG_ENDIAN and PWS_LITTLE_ENDIAN are mutually exclusive.
// 2. PWS_BIG_ENDIAN and PWS_LITTLE_ENDIAN may be defined on the complier
//    command line but checks are made to ensure that one and only one is
